data.description: Welcome to this beautiful turn key one-story home. As you enter the home you'll love the upgraded luxury vinyl flooring and neutral interior paint throughout.  An open concept with two living rooms and large an office or 4th bedroom. Enjoy cooking and entertaining in this updated kitchen with Quartz countertops, ample cabinets with counter space and walk-in pantry. The primary suite is spacious offers natural light filtered through a double door access to the pool, ensuite features a double vanity, walk-in shower, and large closet. Secondary bedrooms with a full bathroom across from the hallway. The covered patio overlooks a low-maintenance backyard and a Salt water poo for great outdoor entertainment. Wait a fruit tree of grape vines to eat and/or make homemade wine. Recently repaired the foundation and installed sods in the front yard. This home is conveniently located to Randolph AFB, Fort Sam Houston, IH35, 1604, and downtown Cibolo where there are great restaurants and entertainment!
